				<td colspan="2"><span>No pet can tank if there is a PC in melee range. Charmed pets themselves are completely ignored if there is more than four creatures on the aggro list; essentially, you can have a max of two charmers working together on any given mob, if you want a pet to tank. 
<br />

<br />
It should be noted that not all mobs duel wield either, although it's usually a case of trial and error to see what does and what doesn't. For example, the dire charmeable elementals in BoT do not dual wield, but the higher level elementals do.</span></td>
